<br>
<center>
<span style="font-weight: bold;">2025 January 04 & 06:   MAC moves to new training space</span>
</center>
<br>
<br><br>

On Saturday, January 4th, the MAC held its last class in squash court #3 of the Makati (Sports) Club, the space we had called home since 05 March 2007. After this class, MAC members removed 264 of the club's tatami material from squash court #3 and carried them to our new training space, some 20 meters away. This final class was led by Chief Instructor Dam Amaranto.<br><br>

Members moved the remaining 35 jigsaw mats to the new space on Monday, January 6th. After these final pieces were installed, the first session in the new location was held, led by club Administrator R.S. Reyes.<br><br>

The old space we had occupied for 18 years had 88sqm of tatami area. The new space is 72sqm of training surface.<br><br><br><br>



